Norway Boosts Mongstad Carbon-Storage Site Cost to $985 Million

-- B y   M a r i a n n e   S t i g s e t
-- 
2011-10-06T08:28:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/norway-boosts-mongstad-carbon-storage-site-cost-to-985-million.html
Norway revised the cost estimate for
the Mongstad carbon capture and storage test center up by 257
million kroner to 5.77 billion kroner ($985 million), the
Ministry of Petroleum and Energy said today in a statement on
its website in connection with the 2012 budget bill. The test
center is 80 percent complete and will start operating next
year, it said.  The government is allocating 1.7 billion kroner to the test
center in 2012, the ministry said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marianne Stigset at 
 mstigset@bloomberg.net  